13101.name: Tide Turner
13101.desc: Significantly increases the DMG dealt with the third strike of the normal attack. Enemies hit are afflicted with Stun.

13102.name: Shield Spin
13102.desc: Throws out an additional shield with Skill 1: Shield Throw.

13103.name: Energy Strike
13103.desc: Hold down on the normal attack button during the second strike of a normal attack and release the second strike again by expending Divine Grace.

13104.name: Scorching Strike
13104.desc: Hits landed with the second strike of the normal attack inflict Scorch on the enemy.

13105.name: Strike & Charge
13105.desc: Normal attacks grant additional Divine Grace.

13106.name: Gather Them in
13106.desc: Using Skill 3: Protection of Faith will gather nearby enemies.

13107.name: Flying Shield Strike
13107.desc: Using Skill 3: Protection of Faith will throw a shield at nearby enemies.

13108.name: Life-Giving Shield
13108.desc: Hits landed with the shield restore HP.

13109.name: Sword Offense
13109.desc: Normal attacks shorten all existing skill CDs.

13110.name: Faith Anew
13110.desc: Skill 3: Protection of Faith is unleashed one more time.

13111.name: Counter Guard
13111.desc: A successful counterattack will trigger Skill 3: Protection of Faith.

13112.name: Freeze Guard
13112.desc: Hits landed with the shield inflict Freeze on enemies hit.

13113.name: Wind Pursuit
13113.desc: The final strike of a normal attack triggers Hurricane.

13114.name: Girding Wind
13114.desc: Hits landed with Hurricane grant Super Armor for a short time as well as restore HP.

13115.name: Tracking Crystals
13115.desc: Triggers Sacred Gale Crystals on enemies hit by Hurricane.

13116.name: Power Crystals
13116.desc: Increases the DMG dealt by Sacred Gale Crystals.

13117.name: Strengthening Wind
13117.desc: Grants Super Armor during normal attacks.

13118.name: Cloudrush Whirl
13118.desc: Significantly increases the speed of normal attacks.

13119.name: Breaking Force
13119.desc: Triggers Sacred Gale Crystals on all enemies on the field when an enemy is defeated.

13120.name: Hunter's Wind
13120.desc: Landing a hit with Sacred Gale Crystals triggers the same effect another 2 times.

13121.name: Charged and Ready
13121.desc: Normal attacks shorten the CD of Skill 3: Breach, and the last strike of a normal attack grants 1 Trace.

13123.name: Time After Time
13123.desc: Using Skill 3: Breach gathers nearby enemies and also triggers the same effect one more time.

13124.name: Shock & Protect
13124.desc: Hits landed with Skill 3: Breach inflict Stun on enemies hit as well as generate a shield for the Mod.

13125.name: Moon Phase
13125.desc: Hits landed with normal attacks shorten all existing skill CDs.

13127.name: Fire Moon
13127.desc: Hits landed with Saku inflict Scorch on the enemy.

13128.name: Moongazer
13128.desc: Hits landed with the last strike Saku: Moonlit Night inflicts Freeze on the enemy.

13129.name: Blade Dance Frenzy
13129.desc: Significantly increases the speed of normal attacks.

13130.name: Rearward Blade Throw
13130.desc: Dodges at the fourth strike of the normal attack and throws out Saku.

13131.name: Back to the Untainted Heart
13131.desc: Hits landed with Saku restore HP.

13133.name: Defensive Focus
13133.desc: Triggers Super Armor, which disappears 1s after taking a hit. Effect refreshes once every 10s.

13134.name: Flash and Slash
13134.desc: Dodges at the second strike of the normal attack and expends 30 Divine Grace to trigger Skill 2: Bo: Lunar Eclipse.

13135.name: Full Gathering
13135.desc: Saku will gather nearby enemies upon hit.

13136.name: Heavy Blade Strike
13136.desc: Becomes slowed, though DMG dealt also significantly increases.

13137.name: Shadow Leaper
13137.desc: Following a successful block, the block-counterattack is replaced with Skill 2: Ripple of Fate.

13138.name: Blazing Fire
13138.desc: Hits landed with Skill 2 inflict Scorch on the enemy.

13139.name: Dimglare Domain
13139.desc: After triggering the Decision state, slowly gathers surrounding enemies in front of the Mod.

13140.name: Another Daybreak
13140.desc: Increases all DMG dealt when in the Decision state.

13141.name: Sword of Determination
13141.desc: Grants Super Armor during normal attacks.

13142.name: Sharp Severance
13142.desc: Increases the Mod Index Multiplier slightly when in the Decision state.

13143.name: Daylight Glow
13143.desc: Restores HP over time when in the Decision state.

13145.name: Time Potential
13145.desc: Normal attacks grant additional Divine Grace.

13146.name: Zero-Hour Flow
13146.desc: Normal attacks shorten all existing skill CDs.

13147.name: Sword Speed-Up
13147.desc: Significantly increases the speed of normal attacks launched in the Decision state.

13148.name: Instant Dawn
13148.desc: Grants Daybreak when the Ultimate Skill: Resolve of the Moment is used.
